Package tw.funnymph.commons.sort

This package contains the interfaces and classes for multi-sorting.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SortDescriptor<InputType>
    This interface extends Transformer to provide additional information about how to sort elements.
    Transformer<InputType,OutputType>
    This interface defines the method to transform the input instance to the instance of another type.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSortDescriptor<InputType>
    This abstract class provides the common implementation of SortDescriptor.
    PropertySortDescriptor<InputType>
    This class provides an implementation that uses the given property name to obtain the comparable part from a object.
    SimpleSortDescriptor<InputType,T extends Comparable<T>>
    This class simply wraps a Transformer instance as a sort descriptor.
    SortDescriptors<InputType>
    This class provides a set of methods to organize sort descriptors together to sort elements.
    SortUtils
    This class provides a set of methods to sort elements in Java Collection with sort descriptors.
